{"tid":1637802,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[突發] South Park 官方正式向中國道歉","createTime":"2019-10-08T05:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T02:28:03.000Z","uid":147785,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"546c76289e07eeedae6420de089e2137039c3739","tid":1637802,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yhZaG0n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyhZaG0n.jpg&h=955764f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n來自Trey Parker與Matt Stone向中國的正式道歉<br />\n就跟NBA一樣，我們非常歡迎中國式和諧深入我們的家園與心中。<br />\n我們也一樣愛錢更勝自由與民主。習主席長的一點也不像小熊維尼。<br />\n本週三晚間10點，請準時收看我們的第300集動畫。<br />\n中國共產黨萬歲！預祝您今秋高粱豐收！我們這樣算和好了嗎中國？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd28dec8cafddc61690f36d3d5a58d18f57ab6cf","tid":1637802,"uid":67329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:56:03.000Z","msg":"「突發」衰仔樂園(South Park)發出官方聲明向支那跪低<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1636671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/163667